{"word":"G1163 - δεῖ - deî - die - Behoved","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">δεῖ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">deî</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">die</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Behoved</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வேண்டியதாயிரு. அவசியமென்றிரு"},{"paragraph":"it is necessary"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Third person singular active present of <a href=\"#/G1210 - δέω - déō - deh'-o/1210\">G1210</a>; also <b>&#x03B4;&#x03B5;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03BD;</b> <b>deon</b> which is neuter active participle of the same; both used impersonally; <i>it is</i> (<i>was</i>, etc.) <i>necessary</i> (as <i>binding</i>): - behoved, be meet, must (needs), (be) need (-ful), ought, should.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}